The paper deals with dynamic pricing in competitive markets, which is a topic that falls under game theory (cs.GT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of algorithms to maximize revenue suggests a focus on optimization (cs.DS) and the technical properties mentioned in the paper suggest a focus on mathematical analysis (cs.MA). Finally, the paper deals with consumer utilities and demand, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
